title: Mobile payments company Square plans IPO
text:
Photo: Bill Pugliano / Bill Pugliano / Getty Images 2013 Jack Dorsey leads both Twitter and Square. Jack Dorsey leads both Twitter and Square.
Electronic payments company Square announced Wednesday that it will pursue an initial public offering, selling shares under the ticker symbol SQ. Jack Dorsey leads both Twitter and Square. Jack Dorsey leads both Twitter and Square.
